# Implementation Plan: Mobile Optimization & Branding Fix

This plan addresses the mobile display issues and simplifies the branding from "zget Portal" to "zget".

## Mobile Audit Findings

From the mobile inspection (375x667, iPhone SE):

### Critical Issues

1. **Header Completely Broken**
   - All elements (logo, ingest input, archive button, vault link, settings) crammed on one line
   - Ingest input squeezed to ~20% width, unusable
   - Placeholder text severely clipped
   - Zero padding between elements

2. **Branding Incorrect**
   - Header shows "zget Portal" instead of "zget"
   - Page title is "zget | Portal" instead of "zget"

3. **Settings Modal Not Responsive**
   - 2-column grid doesn't stack on mobile
   - Inputs cramped
   - Button placement disconnected

4. **Content Spacing**
   - Search input awkwardly positioned
   - Video card text lacks padding

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] App Header

#### [MODIFY] [app.js](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/static/components/app.js)

**Branding:**
- Change "zget Portal" to "zget" in header

**Mobile Responsive:**
- Add media query for `@media (max-width: 768px)`
- Stack header elements vertically on mobile
- Move ingest input to its own row below the header
- Increase ingest input to 100% width on mobile
- Adjust spacing and padding for touch targets

### [Component] Settings Modal

#### [MODIFY] [settings.js](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/static/components/settings.js)

**Mobile Responsive:**
- Change `.form-grid` to stack single column on mobile: `grid-template-columns: 1fr`
- Increase modal max-width to 95% on mobile
- Center the "Commit Changes" button
- Stack LAN Access badge and URL vertically if needed

### [Document] Page Title

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/static/index.html)

- Change `<title>zget | Portal</title>` to `<title>zget</title>`

### [Component] Vault Grid

#### [MODIFY] [vault.js](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/static/components/vault.js)

**Mobile Responsive:**
- Ensure video cards have proper side padding on mobile
- Stack search input below "The Vault" heading on mobile
- Adjust grid columns to 1 column on mobile if not already

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification (Browser)
- Open Portal at mobile width (375px, 667px)
- Verify header elements stack properly
- Verify ingest input is full width and usable
- Verify settings modal is readable and usable
- Tap through all interactive elements
- Take screenshots of fixed mobile layout
